310
00:26:10,880 --> 00:26:12,079
Hal ini amat serius,

311
00:26:12,479 --> 00:26:14,040
Maharaja Syurga, tolong buat keputusan.

312
00:26:14,479 --> 00:26:15,719
Siapa?

313
00:26:16,520 --> 00:26:18,000
Syaitan Naga terakhir

314
00:26:18,119 --> 00:26:19,680
